rows.label: qev055901_MSG0001
rows.name:
This can't possibly be a natural phenomenon.
We have to intervene.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0002
rows.name:
Just weeks ago, there were hardly any of them in
Cauldros! But now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0010
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask what Julius is talking about.

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0020
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask who "them" is.

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0003
rows.name: The visigel population is growing in Cauldros.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0004
rows.name:
They're normally very slow to multiply, as indigens go,
but lately they've been spreading like clover.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0005
rows.name:
Oh, and they're also extremely aggressive,
which isn't any fun at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0006
rows.name:
If they keep growing at this rate, it will make work in
Cauldros extremely difficult for us BLADEs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0007
rows.name: Visigels. They're indigens over in Cauldros.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0008
rows.name:
Lately, their population has started to grow at an
unnatural rate. They're usually very slow to multiply,
so something is definitely not right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0009
rows.name:
Oh, and they're also extremely aggressive,
if I didn't mention that yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0010
rows.name:
If they keep growing at this rate, it will make work in
Cauldros extremely difficult for us BLADEs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0011
rows.name: If you have time, I'd love your help in investigating.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0012
rows.name:
I'll need a tissue sample first, if you can head out there
and round one up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0013
rows.name:
Come back with that sample once you have it.
I'll be waiting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0014
rows.name:
Please hunt down a visigel and bring me a tissue
sample, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0015
rows.name:
Thanks for the good work.
Unfortunately, something's still not right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0016
rows.name:
According to the latest FrontierNav data,
the visigel population has risen by two.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0017
rows.name:
But it should be down one, thanks to you.
...What in the heck is going on here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0030
rows.name: Propose[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0031
rows.name:
Offer to bring Julius more samples
to help find the answer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0040
rows.name: Assert[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0041
rows.name:
Say that something must be actively
causing the visigel population to rise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0018
rows.name:
Thank you. It really is bizarre.
Visigels simply shouldn't be breeding like this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0019
rows.name:
If we're going to figure out what's happening,
we'll need those extra tissue samples.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0020
rows.name:
It really is bizarre. Visigels simply shouldn't be
breeding in these numbers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0021
rows.name:
If we hope to figure out what's happening,
we're going to need more tissue samples.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0022
rows.name:
Sorry to send you back out to Cauldros, but samples
from two more visigels would be a big help in getting
to the bottom of this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0023
rows.name:
Collect tissue samples from two visigels,
then bring them back here to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0024
rows.name: ...What? That's not... This shouldn't be possible![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0025
rows.name:
The visigel numbers are up again! This time FrontierNav
is saying there are four more. What in the hell...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0050
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask what Julius's analysis has turned up.

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0060
rows.name: Observe

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0061
rows.name: Say there must be some secret to the visigel life cycle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0026
rows.name:
Well, there are some irregularities in the blood,
but I still haven't pinned down exactly what's going on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0027
rows.name:
I suppose it's possible, but this sort of behavior has
never been seen before. There must be some immediate
cause. Some prompt.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0028
rows.name:
Rapidly multiplying organisms...
Yes, I've seen something like it before.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0029
rows.name:
Can I possibly trouble you for four more samples,
[ST:playername ]?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0030
rows.name:
This mystery's too big for me to handle alone.
I'm going to see about getting some help while you're
off in Cauldros.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0031
rows.name: Good luck to the both of us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0032
rows.name:
I know it's a lot to ask, but please bring me four more
visigel tissue samples.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0033
rows.name:
The anomaly was more than one human could puzzle
through, so I reached out to the Orphe for help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0034
rows.name:
I suppose this is what you humans would call a
"bad feeling."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0035
rows.name:
I have been analyzing the visigel samples since Julius
came to me, and I am concerned.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0036
rows.name:
I worry that this phenomenon may have serious
implications for the Orphe's very existence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0037
rows.name:
However, I must be extremely cautious and thorough in
my work. As such, I require more samples.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0038
rows.name:
Well, they won't be hard to findâ€”the damn buggers
are multiplying again, somehow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0039
rows.name: Tissue samples from six more individuals should do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0040
rows.name:
That should be enough to reach a conclusion.
I only hope it will not be a grim one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0070
rows.name: Inquire about Theories

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0071
rows.name: Ask if Han'barac has a hypothesis.

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0080
rows.name: Inquire about Conclusions

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0081
rows.name: Ask what exactly a "grim conclusion" would entail.

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0041
rows.name:
I would prefer not to speculate until I am more
certain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0042
rows.name:
Putting off things you don't want to deal with isn't very
logical. Nice to see us humans and you Orpheans have
that in common.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0043
rows.name:
I...would prefer not to discuss it yet.
Thinking about it fills my mind with confusion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0044
rows.name: You Orphe feel that way sometimes too, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0045
rows.name:
One last round of tissue samples should get us to the
bottom of this. So yeah, we need six more, please.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0046
rows.name:
I know this has been a lot of work,
and I appreciate it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0047
rows.name:
One last round of visigel tissue samples should give us
our answer. We need six more, please.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0048
rows.name: Does it look like you'll get your answer, Han'barac?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0049
rows.name: ...Has the visigel population continued to expand?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0050
rows.name: 'Fraid so.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0051
rows.name:
I suspected as much. I have never felt this way before.
Never felt this...gloom, I suppose you would call it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0052
rows.name:
The visigel tissue analysis results, combined with the
fact that their numbers continue to grow, makes it
conclusive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0053
rows.name:
Though I am shocked, to be frank.
It is a conclusion I did not wish to think possible...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0090
rows.name: Inquire about Conclusions

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0091
rows.name: Ask what Han'barac has learned.

rows.label: qev055901_JNK0100
rows.name: Inquire about Shock

rows.label: qev055901_SEL0101
rows.name: Ask why Han'barac is so surprised.

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0054
rows.name:
The Ovah my kind reveres and obeys also exists within
the bodies of these visigels.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0055
rows.name:
The Ovah my kind reveres and obeys also exists within
the bodies of these primitive visigels.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0056
rows.name: This is a most shocking revelation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0057
rows.name: And this Ovah you talk about is...what, exactly?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055901_MSG0058
rows.name:
It is a virus that exists within the bodies of the Orphe,
but further explanation can wait. For now, we need to
formulate a plan to deal with this new development.[ST:wait ]
